snippet.title: Tetraphopia - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1886080/Tetraphobia/

Tetraphobia is an action rougelite set in a stylized world of floating islands. Utilise different bows to shoot, dash, blast and loot your way through different realms. Filled with unique enemies, bosses, artefacts and NPCs every venture into the fractured sky is it's own unique challenge.
